@startuml UC-08_Handle_Error

title UC-08: Handle Error - Sequence Diagram

skinparam SequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam SequenceArrowColor #C62828
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF

participant ExecutionService
participant "Error Handler" as ErrorHandler
participant NotificationService
participant AuditService
participant Database as DB

ExecutionService -> ErrorHandler: 1. Error caught: {type, message, stack}
ErrorHandler -> ErrorHandler: 2. Classify error (CRITICAL/ERROR/WARNING)
ErrorHandler -> DB: 3. Log error record
DB --> ErrorHandler: 4. Error logged
ErrorHandler -> NotificationService: 5. Create notification
NotificationService -> DB: 6. Store notification
DB --> NotificationService: 7. Stored
ErrorHandler -> AuditService: 8. Log audit entry
AuditService -> DB: 9. Store audit log
DB --> AuditService: 10. Logged
ErrorHandler --> ExecutionService: 11. Return {retry_policy, notification_sent}

@enduml
